{"tid":2008539,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關酷刑","createTime":"2020-05-09T06:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T19:08:08.000Z","uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e036eab426cf038b08ca1d5b0ca38bd05b7785e2","tid":2008539,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:10:03.000Z","msg":"人類一般不會花心思去為動物製造酷刑，但卻會為人類花盡心思，錢財，時間，去設計同行駛使酷刑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國的凌遲是其表表者，可以說是人類酷刑史上的極致<br />\n<br />\n跟據中國凌遲酷刑多年的行駛使經驗，受刑者受刑之時，雖氣若遊絲，未能反抗，但時以眼神目光望住繪子手，我諗呢個係一個反制，當然繪子手亦有反制方法，可以行使&rdquo;剜目凌迟&ldquo;，即挖掉雙眼，似是大家在&ldquo;鬧法&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n如果受刑者快死，有時會被人餵食食物，或休一休息，甚致給他止一止痛<br />\n<br />\n明朝宦官劉謹，就類似這樣，因為&ldquo;拖延死亡&rdquo;的工夫做得完善，以致劉謹受刑達數日，在斷氣前一刻，他的身體幾乎被削到如一幅骨架<br />\n<br />\n不可有豬，牛，老虎，白鴿等等被人拿起凌遲示眾吧?"},{"pid":"6db9d0751d7fb325bc54556aee0456127e335ad6","tid":2008539,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=zGsG5gKf4oE&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzGsG5gKf4oE%26feature%3Dshare&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=5f82ebb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=zGsG5gKf4oE&amp;feature=share</a>"},{"pid":"4259076aaed795e4823fa76e1335ef12a609c6bc","tid":2008539,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6db9d0751d7fb325bc54556aee0456127e335ad6","tid":2008539,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=zGsG5gKf4oE&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzGsG5gKf4oE%26feature%3Dshare&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=5f82ebb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=zGsG5gKf4oE&amp;feature=share</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:08:08.000